#

Caprese Salad with Fresh Mozzarella and Basil

10 min
$8
400 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SaladAppetizerFresh

Description

A refreshing and vibrant salad featuring creamy mozzarella and fragrant basil, perfect for a light meal or appetizer.

Ingredients

  • fresh mozzarella: 8 ounces
  • tomatoes: 2 large
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
